  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('Franck', 'franck', false, 'FRANCK is here for a gid time, no a long time. Club goers have said that his sets are hotter than a Greggs Steak Bake just out the oven and his tunes are harder than Blighty’s Boozers. All bants, luv yez x

Franck FKA VIGILE has established himself as a key player in the electro and techno scene over the last couple of years. His debut EP release with London label Childsplay got him off to a good start, bagging a premiere with Mixmag and claiming DJ Mags Electro release of the month in their magazine. His subsequent releases garnered him more fans and helped him get his first international booking in France. 

The pandemic has given him time to transition into his new alias, Franck, where he has shifted his focus more towards the harder and faster style of techno. The new tracks have already received support from top DJ''s such as SPFDJ, Jensen Interceptor, and OTTA to name a few and he shows no sign of stopping with a busy release schedule planned. 

The Scottish DJ and Producer also heads the label Carouse which has had some killer releases since its inception - notably a stand-out electro EP from Shawn Cartier and a full-throttle techno EP from Irish Duo, Riot Code. It''s exciting to see what sort of damage he can bring to the club when we see them return in 2021.', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/franck/386082/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'FRANCK is here for a gid time, no a long time. Club goers have said that his sets are hotter than a Greggs Steak Bake just out the oven and his tunes are harder than Blighty’s Boozers. All bants, luv yez x

