The pandemic has given him time to transition into his new alias, Franck, where he has shifted his focus more towards the harder and faster style of techno. The new tracks have already received support from top DJ''s such as SPFDJ, Jensen Interceptor, and OTTA to name a few and he shows no sign of stopping with a busy release schedule planned. 

The Scottish DJ and Producer also heads the label Carouse which has had some killer releases since its inception - notably a stand-out electro EP from Shawn Cartier and a full-throttle techno EP from Irish Duo, Riot Code. It''s exciting to see what sort of damage he can bring to the club when we see them return in 2021.')
