  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('Lobster', 'lobster', false, 'Dutch DJ and producer Lobster is another example of Amsterdam’s visionary and fertile underground scene. Emerging from the notorious rave community through his former residency at Orphic Amsterdam, where he perfected the craft of playing dance floor and storyline inspired techno, this current Vault Sessions resident knows how to adapt to any crowd. 

Combined with his unconditional passion for electronic music, it is certain Lobster is a force to be reckoned with. With a musical library spanning multiple sub-genres, tempos, and decades, Lobster always has the fitting track ready to be played out, scouting the dance floor for the perfect moment. His strong work ethic and keen sense of the crowd have led him to play sets for hungry audiences in venues all across the globe, like a 12-hours closing set at Bassiani, Awakenings, Freedom Medellin, Reaktor, Basement New York, Gotec and many more. 

After focusing on playing music rather than producing it himself, he started to write his own music in his studio since a few years. He focusses on hypnotising, trippy techno which is very in line with the sound he pushes as a DJ. Until now he has successfully released his stellar creations on solid labels like Room Trax, Format, Warok and Oecus.', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/lobster/199697/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'Dutch DJ and producer Lobster is another example of Amsterdam’s visionary and fertile underground scene. Emerging from the notorious rave community through his former residency at Orphic Amsterdam, where he perfected the craft of playing dance floor and storyline inspired techno, this current Vault Sessions resident knows how to adapt to any crowd. 

Combined with his unconditional passion for electronic music, it is certain Lobster is a force to be reckoned with. With a musical library spanning multiple sub-genres, tempos, and decades, Lobster always has the fitting track ready to be played out, scouting the dance floor for the perfect moment. His strong work ethic and keen sense of the crowd have led him to play sets for hungry audiences in venues all across the globe, like a 12-hours closing set at Bassiani, Awakenings, Freedom Medellin, Reaktor, Basement New York, Gotec and many more. 

After focusing on playing music rather than producing it himself, he started to write his own music in his studio since a few years. He focusses on hypnotising, trippy techno which is very in line with the sound he pushes as a DJ. Until now he has successfully released his stellar creations on solid labels like Room Trax, Format, Warok and Oecus.')
