  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('Paige Tomlinson', 'paige tomlinson', false, 'A name you may have heard of by now, Paige Tomlinson is a dynamic DJ hailing from Liverpool, renowned for her high-energy and euphoric sets heavily influenced by the 90s era. Her rich musical knowledge and technical prowess is continuing to turn heads.

With a debut release on Archie Hamilton''s Microhertz and two EPs released on Dansu Discs, Paige has firmly established herself in the electronic music scene and continues to craft a sound that pays homage to the golden era.

Paige has graced the decks at some of the world''s most renowned venues, including Amnesia Ibiza, Hi Ibiza, After Caposile, Warehouse Project, and Fabric London. Her electrifying performances have also been a highlight at major festivals such as Glastonbury, Creamfields, Secret Garden Party, Beatherder, Forbidden Forest, and Hide & Seek. Beyond the UK, her music has also resonated with audiences worldwide, with her completing a tour of Australia and Asia as well as playing in countries such as Brazil, Croatia, Malta, the Netherlands, France, and Egypt, to name a few.

Paige''s performances have the power to transport audiences through yesteryears, creating unforgettable musical journeys that resonate long after the last track has played. With plenty of exciting plans yet to be announced and continuing to craft a unique sound which cements her place within the electronic music scene, the future is bright for Paige Tomlinson.', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/paige-tomlinson/386633/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'A name you may have heard of by now, Paige Tomlinson is a dynamic DJ hailing from Liverpool, renowned for her high-energy and euphoric sets heavily influenced by the 90s era. Her rich musical knowledge and technical prowess is continuing to turn heads.

With a debut release on Archie Hamilton''s Microhertz and two EPs released on Dansu Discs, Paige has firmly established herself in the electronic music scene and continues to craft a sound that pays homage to the golden era.

Paige has graced the decks at some of the world''s most renowned venues, including Amnesia Ibiza, Hi Ibiza, After Caposile, Warehouse Project, and Fabric London. Her electrifying performances have also been a highlight at major festivals such as Glastonbury, Creamfields, Secret Garden Party, Beatherder, Forbidden Forest, and Hide & Seek. Beyond the UK, her music has also resonated with audiences worldwide, with her completing a tour of Australia and Asia as well as playing in countries such as Brazil, Croatia, Malta, the Netherlands, France, and Egypt, to name a few.

Paige''s performances have the power to transport audiences through yesteryears, creating unforgettable musical journeys that resonate long after the last track has played. With plenty of exciting plans yet to be announced and continuing to craft a unique sound which cements her place within the electronic music scene, the future is bright for Paige Tomlinson.')
