  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('Marsolo', 'marsolo', false, 'Marijn van Vliet, better known as Marsolo, is a house DJ and producer, born and raised in The Netherlands. His life took a musical turn when he started stacking drum loops on his computer. 

Year by year, he became more and more professional at music production. After finishing highschool, he started at the well-respected Herman Brood Academy; the perfect chance to settle his name in the international house scene. 

A typical Marsolo track provokes feelings of euphoria and is recognized by vintage, sample-based drums, complemented by warm, refreshing synths. Marsolo adds emotion to his music and DJ sets by telling a musical story to be freely interpreted by the listener. His mission is to strike a chord with the crowd. In the studio and on stage, Marsolo isn’t afraid to break rules. His creativity already led to releases on well-known labels, like Eastenderz, House of Love, and PIV, only to name a few. By constantly finding innovative ways to create music, his future releases will always be surprising.

Being discovered and supported by well-known DJs, like Chris Stussy, East End Dubs and Folamour, his schedule is expanding rapidly. By already having played at renowned venues like Thuishaven and Paradiso, his future looks brighter every day. Keep an eye on Marsolo becausehe has just embarked on a long musical journey.', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/marsolo/386609/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'Marijn van Vliet, better known as Marsolo, is a house DJ and producer, born and raised in The Netherlands. His life took a musical turn when he started stacking drum loops on his computer. 

Year by year, he became more and more professional at music production. After finishing highschool, he started at the well-respected Herman Brood Academy; the perfect chance to settle his name in the international house scene. 

A typical Marsolo track provokes feelings of euphoria and is recognized by vintage, sample-based drums, complemented by warm, refreshing synths. Marsolo adds emotion to his music and DJ sets by telling a musical story to be freely interpreted by the listener. His mission is to strike a chord with the crowd. In the studio and on stage, Marsolo isn’t afraid to break rules. His creativity already led to releases on well-known labels, like Eastenderz, House of Love, and PIV, only to name a few. By constantly finding innovative ways to create music, his future releases will always be surprising.

Being discovered and supported by well-known DJs, like Chris Stussy, East End Dubs and Folamour, his schedule is expanding rapidly. By already having played at renowned venues like Thuishaven and Paradiso, his future looks brighter every day. Keep an eye on Marsolo becausehe has just embarked on a long musical journey.')
