  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('Nico Moreno', 'nico moreno', false, 'Nico Moreno is a French DJ and producer from Caen, recognized as one of the major
players in the contemporary industrial techno rave scene. He began producing music at a
young age, creating intense music characterized by fast, hard-hitting kicks.

Nico Moreno quickly made himself known thanks to songs which all met with resounding
success, leaving his mark on the techno scene. Titles such as "Purple Widow," "Insolent
Rave," "Techno Crari," "Your Bad Company," "This is for my haters," among many others,
have all enjoyed dazzling success, helping to consolidate his reputation as an essential
producer. Many other compositions by Nico Moreno have captivated techno fans with
innovative sounds and catchy rhythms. These tracks have become essential anthems in the
world of electronic music, propelling Nico Moreno to the heart of the contemporary techno
scene.

His ability to create repeat hits, experiment with sounds, and push the genre''s boundaries
have solidified his position as a pillar of electronic music. Each track reflects his passion for
music and his commitment to providing a unique experience to his audience, which has
earned him well-deserved recognition within the global techno community.

His path to success was difficult. He had to take on the challenge of finding a place in a
demanding industry, requiring sacrifice and unfailing commitment. Nico has delved deep into
techno to craft a unique style, blending catchy kicks and captivating sounds at explosive
speed. Despite the many challenges and daring sacrifices, Nico created authentic music full
of passion and innovation. As the founder of Insolent Rave Records, he is committed to
supporting young talents and redefining the future of electronic music.

In 2024, Nico Moreno is releasing his debut album, “You Can''t Stop The Movement”. This
highly anticipated album marks a significant milestone in his career, promising to deliver the
intense, innovative sounds that have made him a standout figure in the techno world.', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/nico-moreno/271590/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'Nico Moreno is a French DJ and producer from Caen, recognized as one of the major
players in the contemporary industrial techno rave scene. He began producing music at a
young age, creating intense music characterized by fast, hard-hitting kicks.

Nico Moreno quickly made himself known thanks to songs which all met with resounding
success, leaving his mark on the techno scene. Titles such as "Purple Widow," "Insolent
Rave," "Techno Crari," "Your Bad Company," "This is for my haters," among many others,
have all enjoyed dazzling success, helping to consolidate his reputation as an essential
producer. Many other compositions by Nico Moreno have captivated techno fans with
innovative sounds and catchy rhythms. These tracks have become essential anthems in the
world of electronic music, propelling Nico Moreno to the heart of the contemporary techno
scene.

His ability to create repeat hits, experiment with sounds, and push the genre''s boundaries
have solidified his position as a pillar of electronic music. Each track reflects his passion for
music and his commitment to providing a unique experience to his audience, which has
earned him well-deserved recognition within the global techno community.

His path to success was difficult. He had to take on the challenge of finding a place in a
demanding industry, requiring sacrifice and unfailing commitment. Nico has delved deep into
techno to craft a unique style, blending catchy kicks and captivating sounds at explosive
speed. Despite the many challenges and daring sacrifices, Nico created authentic music full
of passion and innovation. As the founder of Insolent Rave Records, he is committed to
supporting young talents and redefining the future of electronic music.

In 2024, Nico Moreno is releasing his debut album, “You Can''t Stop The Movement”. This
highly anticipated album marks a significant milestone in his career, promising to deliver the
intense, innovative sounds that have made him a standout figure in the techno world.')
