  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('Innellea', 'innellea', false, 'Innellea – a neologism; created in reference to musical reinvention. Neither restrained nor bound by conventions, Innellea’s visions and impressions are visibly transferred into music.
The Munich-based live act, DJ and producer combines melancholic, cinematic soundscapes and a distinct, percussive touch in his unique and abstract sound. The result is an intimate listening experience which hovers between melodic introspection and explosive, post-apocalyptic club music.
He took the scene by storm in 2019, leaving a dusty cloud in his wake. Innellea was first a secret weapon for some of the techno scene’s leading DJs, before his music was released via Afterlife, Innervisions and Diynamic. From then on, Innellea’s colourful and intricate rhythms captivated crowds worldwide. Tracks like ‘Vigilans’, ‘Forced to Bend’ and ‘The World Returns’ are good examples of the bold musical statements which define the project. From the success of his releases came live sets and a wealth of unreleased tracks, creating a global hype around his name. Innellea continues to rewrite the rulebook with each release and live performance.
Whenever in need of driving spheres, impulsive vibes and touches of genuine feeling, Innellea’s music will be there. Just in time to broaden your mindset.', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/innellea/205860/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'Innellea – a neologism; created in reference to musical reinvention. Neither restrained nor bound by conventions, Innellea’s visions and impressions are visibly transferred into music.
The Munich-based live act, DJ and producer combines melancholic, cinematic soundscapes and a distinct, percussive touch in his unique and abstract sound. The result is an intimate listening experience which hovers between melodic introspection and explosive, post-apocalyptic club music.
He took the scene by storm in 2019, leaving a dusty cloud in his wake. Innellea was first a secret weapon for some of the techno scene’s leading DJs, before his music was released via Afterlife, Innervisions and Diynamic. From then on, Innellea’s colourful and intricate rhythms captivated crowds worldwide. Tracks like ‘Vigilans’, ‘Forced to Bend’ and ‘The World Returns’ are good examples of the bold musical statements which define the project. From the success of his releases came live sets and a wealth of unreleased tracks, creating a global hype around his name. Innellea continues to rewrite the rulebook with each release and live performance.
Whenever in need of driving spheres, impulsive vibes and touches of genuine feeling, Innellea’s music will be there. Just in time to broaden your mindset.')
