  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('ØTTA', 'øtta', false, 'Øtta seamlessly blends elements of trance and groove to craft a dynamic and vivid musical style. Currently, she offers a fresh take on Brazilian trance with a groovy edge. Her journey from the debut of the "Plus One EP" to the enchanting sounds of "Candy22" showcases Øtta''s ability to infuse old-school psytrance with the rhythmic allure of Brazilian drums, complemented by subtle notes of UK garage.

The ascent of Øtta''s career reached new heights following a stellar performance at Boiler Room, where she not only demonstrated her skill in captivating audiences but also invited them into a captivating realm. In this realm, Øtta''s signature style unfolds a seductiveuniverse characterized by buoyant, warm percussions, rolling basslines, captivating melodies, and the unexpected infusion of vocals. Her artistry transcends traditional boundaries, creating an immersive experience where listeners are drawn into a magneticblend of genres.

Øtta''s music is a testament to her ability to craft a sonic landscape that is both sophisticated and irresistibly danceable, establishing her as a rising force in the realm of electronic music. Since 2024, Øtta has expanded her influence by founding her own labeland event series, Hotties. As both a record label and event planner, Hotties is dedicated to providing a creative outlet for artists to share their music globally, with a hint of spice. Through Hotties, Øtta curates events worldwide, inviting a diverse array of DJs to join her in creating unforgettable experiences for audiences everywhere.

On September 20, 2024, Øtta came back with her EP of four tracks titled “In My 2024 Era,” further showcasing her evolution and creativity in the world of electronic music.This latest project highlights Øtta''s unique proposition, delivering groovy trance with summer vibes and Brazilian/Latino influences, further enhancing her signature sound.', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/otta/370815/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'Øtta seamlessly blends elements of trance and groove to craft a dynamic and vivid musical style. Currently, she offers a fresh take on Brazilian trance with a groovy edge. Her journey from the debut of the "Plus One EP" to the enchanting sounds of "Candy22" showcases Øtta''s ability to infuse old-school psytrance with the rhythmic allure of Brazilian drums, complemented by subtle notes of UK garage.

The ascent of Øtta''s career reached new heights following a stellar performance at Boiler Room, where she not only demonstrated her skill in captivating audiences but also invited them into a captivating realm. In this realm, Øtta''s signature style unfolds a seductiveuniverse characterized by buoyant, warm percussions, rolling basslines, captivating melodies, and the unexpected infusion of vocals. Her artistry transcends traditional boundaries, creating an immersive experience where listeners are drawn into a magneticblend of genres.

Øtta''s music is a testament to her ability to craft a sonic landscape that is both sophisticated and irresistibly danceable, establishing her as a rising force in the realm of electronic music. Since 2024, Øtta has expanded her influence by founding her own labeland event series, Hotties. As both a record label and event planner, Hotties is dedicated to providing a creative outlet for artists to share their music globally, with a hint of spice. Through Hotties, Øtta curates events worldwide, inviting a diverse array of DJs to join her in creating unforgettable experiences for audiences everywhere.

On September 20, 2024, Øtta came back with her EP of four tracks titled “In My 2024 Era,” further showcasing her evolution and creativity in the world of electronic music.This latest project highlights Øtta''s unique proposition, delivering groovy trance with summer vibes and Brazilian/Latino influences, further enhancing her signature sound.')
