						With a discography as versatile as his artistry, the serial hit-maker is no stranger to sensation-level release response. 2022 saw the release of Eli Brown’s massive hit ‘Believe’, which soared to the top of charts at breakneck speed, proving to be an ardent tonesetter for the major year ahead. In 2023, Brown dropped two dynamite releases - his crossover techno track ‘Be the One’ and the infectious lyrical banger ‘Diamonds On My Mind’. Both tracks would ignite viral social media moments, garnering over 100 million cumulative streams / views per release and unequivocally cementing Eli Brown’s status as an underground powerhouse with mainstream appeal.

						With a steady pulse of new music releases and unexpected surprises that will captivate fans and attract millions more on the horizon, 2024 is poised to be one of Brown’s most massive years yet on a storied road to solidifying his positioning as the world’s leading mainstage techno artist.')
