  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('Samoh', 'samoh', false, 'SAMOH is a Techno producer,DJ and live-artist who blends his sound between Techno, Trance and psytrance and you hear this back in his productions and performances.
Step into the sonic realm of SAMOH, a visionary techno trance producer whose existence revolves around an eternal dance with sound. Nestled within the vibrant heartbeat of Rotterdam, SAMOH breathes life into his auditory dreams and dedicates more than half of his conscious hours within the confines of his studio sanctuary, an incubator for his musical evolution.

Metamorphosis has been SAMOH’s constant companion throughout the years. From a little studio in a kitchen to a fully-fledged studio where he can unleash his inspiration. Within these walls, SAMOH metamorphoses raw elements into meticulous soundscapes. Here, dark, entrancing drum patterns emerge, entwined with bouncy basslines, and the ethereal hum of his acid machines weaves an otherworldly tapestry.

Yet, what sets SAMOH apart is his voracious appetite for musical diversity. His work is a mosaic of influences, a kaleidoscope of sonic realms converging into one. The vibrant pulse of Techno, the euphoric waves of Trance, and the hypnotic mind-bending rhythms of Psytrance all converge within SAMOH’s creations. In his live performances and DJ sets, he masterfully blends these sonic dimensions, transporting audiences into uncharted territory where time and space dissolve into a pulsating dance floor.

Samoh’s sonic prowess has ventured beyond the studio, echoed through vinyl releases on the illustrious R-Label Group. His creative prowess further finds expression in his released EPs and singles, resonating through platforms like Innergate, Sindex, Moments in time, Everyone On Acid, and Courtoisy. Across continents, his music reverberates within Clubs, Festivals and peoples minds', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/samoh/386639/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'SAMOH is a Techno producer,DJ and live-artist who blends his sound between Techno, Trance and psytrance and you hear this back in his productions and performances.
Step into the sonic realm of SAMOH, a visionary techno trance producer whose existence revolves around an eternal dance with sound. Nestled within the vibrant heartbeat of Rotterdam, SAMOH breathes life into his auditory dreams and dedicates more than half of his conscious hours within the confines of his studio sanctuary, an incubator for his musical evolution.

Metamorphosis has been SAMOH’s constant companion throughout the years. From a little studio in a kitchen to a fully-fledged studio where he can unleash his inspiration. Within these walls, SAMOH metamorphoses raw elements into meticulous soundscapes. Here, dark, entrancing drum patterns emerge, entwined with bouncy basslines, and the ethereal hum of his acid machines weaves an otherworldly tapestry.

Yet, what sets SAMOH apart is his voracious appetite for musical diversity. His work is a mosaic of influences, a kaleidoscope of sonic realms converging into one. The vibrant pulse of Techno, the euphoric waves of Trance, and the hypnotic mind-bending rhythms of Psytrance all converge within SAMOH’s creations. In his live performances and DJ sets, he masterfully blends these sonic dimensions, transporting audiences into uncharted territory where time and space dissolve into a pulsating dance floor.

Samoh’s sonic prowess has ventured beyond the studio, echoed through vinyl releases on the illustrious R-Label Group. His creative prowess further finds expression in his released EPs and singles, resonating through platforms like Innergate, Sindex, Moments in time, Everyone On Acid, and Courtoisy. Across continents, his music reverberates within Clubs, Festivals and peoples minds')
