  INSERT INTO artists (name, sort_name, is_collective, bio, source_url, bio_source, bio_festival)
  VALUES ('Valody', 'valody', false, 'Originally from Portugal and now based in the Netherlands, Valody is a DJ, producer, promoter, and the driving force behind the Elberec label.
Through her sincerity, unmatched energy and mesmerizing selections, Valody captivates any crowd that dances to her beat. Originally from Portugal and now based in the Netherlands, Valody is a DJ, producer, promoter, and the driving force behind the Elberec label. By amplifying the voices of undiscovered talent and performing at many renowned venues, she has become a key figure in the Portuguese scene. Her dedication hasn’t gone unnoticed in the Netherlands either, where she’s already making waves and recently has joined the infamous Disturbia crew as a resident.

Recognized for her bold choices, she crafts an unstoppable energy on the dance floor that enchants all who join the rhythm. Valody effortlessly weaves between delicate and powerful sounds. Though rooted in techno, her musical approach goes far beyond, exploring a wide range of sounds and moods, making her adapt to any moment. Her passion and commitment shines through, turning her into a distinguished and promising artist.', 'https://www.awakenings.com/en/artists/valody/386645/', 'festival:awakenings-festival-2026', 'Originally from Portugal and now based in the Netherlands, Valody is a DJ, producer, promoter, and the driving force behind the Elberec label.
Through her sincerity, unmatched energy and mesmerizing selections, Valody captivates any crowd that dances to her beat. Originally from Portugal and now based in the Netherlands, Valody is a DJ, producer, promoter, and the driving force behind the Elberec label. By amplifying the voices of undiscovered talent and performing at many renowned venues, she has become a key figure in the Portuguese scene. Her dedication hasn’t gone unnoticed in the Netherlands either, where she’s already making waves and recently has joined the infamous Disturbia crew as a resident.

Recognized for her bold choices, she crafts an unstoppable energy on the dance floor that enchants all who join the rhythm. Valody effortlessly weaves between delicate and powerful sounds. Though rooted in techno, her musical approach goes far beyond, exploring a wide range of sounds and moods, making her adapt to any moment. Her passion and commitment shines through, turning her into a distinguished and promising artist.')
